MQA.ShapeOverlay

Base shape class.  Constructs a new MQA.ShapeOverlay object

Parameters

none

Extends

MQA.Base

Properties

These properties can be manipulated via the MQA.Base.setValue, MQA.Base.setValues, and MQA.Base.getValue functions.

key(string) User-defined key for this object.
color(string) Hex value of the border color.
altColor(string) Hex value of the border alt state color
colorAlpha(float) Opacity of the border (0 - 1).
altColorAlpha(float) Opacity of the border’s alt state (0 - 1).
fillColor(string) Hex value of the fill color.
altFillColor(string) Hex value of the fill alt state color.
fillColorAlpha(float) Opacity of the fill color (0 - 1).
altFillColorAlpha(float) Opacity of the fill color’s alt state (0 - 1).
borderWidth(int) Width of the border in pixels.
altBorderWidth(int) Width of the border’s alt state in pixels.
altStateFlag(boolean) Status of the alt state.
visible(boolean) Visibility of the overlay.
shapePoints(MQA.LatLngCollection) Collection of MQA.LatLng objects to specify the bounds of the objects.
maxZoomLevel(int) Maximum zoom level that the shape will be visible.
minZoomLevel(int) Minimum zoom level that the shape will be visible.
imageURL(string) URL of the image to use (MQA.ImageOverlay only).
imageLevels(array) Array of MQA.ImageLevel specifying image/zoom-level display (MQA.ImageOverlay only).
imageOpacity(float) Opacity of the overlay (MQA.ImageOverlay only).
